# Assalomu alaykum! | Hi There! 👋

**Men Shuhrat Madaminovman** — frontend dasturlashga qiziqadigan, React bilan toza va zamonaviy veb-interfeyslar qurishni yaxshi ko'radigan dasturchiman.

**I'm Shuhrat Madaminov** — a frontend developer who loves building clean, modern web interfaces with React.

---

## 💻 Dasturlash yo'nalishim | My Development Path

- 🌐 **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript — mustahkam poydevor | Solid foundation
- ⚛️ **React.js:** Zamonaviy UI komponentlar yaratish | Building modern UI components
- 🎯 **Maqsadim / Goal:** Sifatli va qulay UI/UX yaratish | Crafting high-quality and user-friendly UI/UX

---

## 🌱 Hozir nimalarni o'rganyapman | What am I learning now?

- ⚛️ React Hooks va State Management | React Hooks and State Management
- 📱 Moslashuvchan (responsive) dizayn | Responsive web design
- ⚡ JavaScript'ni chuqurroq o'rganish | Deepening JavaScript knowledge
- 🗃 Git & GitHub bilan ishlash | Version control with Git & GitHub

---

## 🌟 Maqsadim | My Goal

Men kuchli Frontend dasturchi bo'lish yo'lida qadamma-qadam o'sib bormoqdaman. Har bir loyiha — bu yangi tajriba va rivojlanish uchun ajoyib imkoniyatdir.

I am learning step by step to become a strong Frontend developer. Every project is a new experience and an opportunity to grow.

---

## 🚀 Hozirgi holatim | My Current Status

- 👨‍💻 Junior Frontend dasturchisi | Junior Frontend Developer
- ⚛️ React.js yordamida turli loyihalar quryapman | Building projects with React.js
- 🌍 Loyihalarimni GitHub'da ommaga taqdim etyapman | Publishing my projects on GitHub
- 💡 Izchillik va amaliyotga asosiy e'tiborni qaratyapman | Focusing on consistency and daily practice

